The FS_IOC_FS[SG]ETXATTR ioctls are an alternative to FS_IOC_[GS]ETFLAGS
with additional features. This patch adds support for these ioctls.

Signed-off-by: Sascha Hauer <s.hauer@pengutronix.de>
---
